115
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:54,000
Boom and Papa like that.

116
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:57,000
Oh, thank you, Mama. Snork doesn't like missing his meals.

117
00:07:57,000 --> 00:08:00,000
