233
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:44,000
Ah-ha, you found a ship already, have you?

234
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:49,000
Well, no, there aren't any real sailing ships in Moomin Valley.

235
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:51,000
